description: Beginning to come down from the high of the mountaineering and PR roadie setting over the weekend, I decided it was the time to run my first fantastic four on Strava. That is, the four GoATs of sport as my four most recent uploads. Of course, as follows: the Queens Park four set stunner, the Fort of Bogs, Strathaven torque fest and this, the 2020 OG, the `foot.
